OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA brighter day on Wednesday
OL,6,Fcompared to Tuesday with a mixture of
OL,7,Fcloud and sunny spells. A few showers
OL,8,Fpossible mainly during the morning,
OL,9,Fespecially across Cornwall and north
OL,10,FDevon. Breezy with temperatures near
OL,11,Fnormal.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers mostly easing
OL,14,Fthis evening to leave clearer spells
OL,15,Fovernight. A few showers still
OL,16,Fpossible during the early hours but
OL,17,Fmost places dry. Mild with winds
OL,18,Fstrengthening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
