OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FOften cloudy with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, locally heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes accompanied by strong winds,
OL,8,Fwith the risk of coastal gales. Mild
OL,9,Fby day, but turning colder overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,12,Fon Friday with early rain clearing
OL,13,Ffollowed by frequent, heavy blustery
OL,14,Fshowers, possibly wintry over the
OL,15,Fmoors. Drier Saturday then more rain
OL,16,Fon Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
